data.description: Investors dream.  2 bed and 1 bath home located away from all the traffic, hustle and bustle of city living.  So much possibility. Bring your paint brush and hammer.Fire sprinkler System, a 1000 gallon septic tank. There are 2 separate city water meters. possibilities to build an additional home. 2nd meter, sewer and electric connection installed.  House has wood fencing inside a gated boundary line.  RV parking and lite agriculture as income potential.   Title shows the old house at 46443 St that was demolished. The adjacent lots shows the 46441 St.  Both address sold in 1 lot.
